 *
 * Assume that `<tabs>` component would like to get a list its children `<pane>`

 *
 * ```html
 * <tabs>

 * ```

 *

 * }

 *    <ng-content></ng-content>
 *  `
 * })
 * class Tabs {

 *   constructor(@Query('findme') elList: QueryList<ElementRef>) {...}

 * ```
